X-BEDEWORK-IMAGE-ALT-TEXT:A wide shot of the interior of Duke University C
 hapel during a Sunday morning worship service. On the left\, the congrega
 tion is visible from behind\, seated in pews facing the ornate altar and 
 a large\, vibrant stained-glass window. The high vaulted ceilings and sto
 ne architecture of the chapel are prominent. On the right\, a dark blue o
 verlay contains white text that reads &amp\;amp\;quot\;SUNDAY MORNING WOR
 SHIP SERVICE&amp\;amp\;quot\; in a large\, bold\, sans-serif font.
