DESCRIPTION:<p>Impermanent is multimedia ritual environment combining vide
 o\, sound\, field recordings\, interaction\, zines\, and sensors. Please 
 bring clean trash (soft wrappers\, plastic bags\, compostables\, etc) if 
 you wish to contribute to an interactive artwork.</p>\n<p>Presented by th
 e Critcal Making Working Group\, an FHI graduate working group.</p>
DURATION:PT3H
